Door to door garbage (wet and dry) from all house in all 15 wards under Nagar Panchayat, Shekhopursarai area. pick up earthization from all houses in commercial area, Main market, main road, vegetable market, bus stop and door to door collection,  work partnar, currently in view of covid-19 fogging work done throughout the year.
Complete cleaning , sweeping work, cleaning all main road and commercials area , markets , religious places , main road , vegetable market, bus stops and all small drains of the ward , as well as pick up the waste from the ward to ward the dumping point ( determined by the nagar panchayat) and clean work in both shifts (morning and night) secondary storage sites/dustbin to garbage disposal and dumping area.
